# Project build guidance — BUILDER prompt preamble (example stub)

Copy this file to `build-preamble.md` (drop the `.example`) and REPLACE the body below with your project's
standing rules for the BUILDER. Its contents are injected into **every** builder prompt — unconditionally,
once the file exists (a standing project rule, NOT gated on the task). Absent → no output → identical to stock.

Use it for safety-critical, always-applies rules — things every build must respect regardless of the task.

